      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COOKIE MAN (3) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (19.48) at this track. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won six of nine tries. Yet to miss the placings in four runs from this box, including two wins. Top chance in this line up. SHORTY BOY (8) is an accomplished sprinter with a great record at the short dashes. Was a bit beyond him last time when eighth (25.34) over 450m at Maitland in a NG but is better suited here over less ground. Form at the trip excellent including four wins. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Likely to play a prominent role. IMPERIAL CHOP (1) boasts a strong record this journey here with 12 wins and 11 minors from 30 tries. Was out of the placings last time (19.99) at this track in a Free For All, finishing fifth and beaten 7 lengths. Looks a key chance on best figures. JOCK (4) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can turn the form around.",
